    {
      "idx": 0,
      "start_ms": 3060,
      "end_ms": 8480,
      "text": "난 우리 혜리를 아주 많이 아끼고 사랑해 그",
      "target_text": "I care for and love our Hyeri very much.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0001_3060_8480.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0001_3060_8480.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start_ms": 8480,
      "end_ms": 13940,
      "text": "어떤 잘못을 하더라도 다 덮어주고 싶을만큼 사실",
      "target_text": "No matter what mistakes she makes, I want to cover for her.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0002_8480_13940.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0002_8480_13940.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start_ms": 13940,
      "end_ms": 18780,
      "text": "따지고 보면 딱히 큰 잘못도 아니잖아",
      "target_text": "If you think about it, it's not really a big mistake.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0003_13940_18780.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0003_13940_18780.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start_ms": 18780,
      "end_ms": 23940,
      "text": "그래서 난 이렇게 정리할거야 어떤",
      "target_text": "So I'm going to organize it like this.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0004_18780_23940.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0004_18780_23940.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start_ms": 23940,
      "end_ms": 28580,
      "text": "깡패가 김민지라는 여고생을 납치해서 함께 실종된 사건",
      "target_text": "A thug kidnapped a high school girl named Kim Min-ji, and they both went missing.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0005_23940_28580.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0005_23940_28580.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start_ms": 30180,
      "end_ms": 35160,
      "text": "깡패는 실종됐으니 그럼 이제 김민지",
      "target_text": "Since the thug is missing, now Kim Min-ji just needs to disappear from the world.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0006_30180_35160.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0006_30180_35160.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start_ms": 35160,
      "end_ms": 36940,
      "text": "학생만 세상에서 사라지면 되겠네",
      "target_text": "That would be fine.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0007_35160_36940.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/2b13488bdada4a049c564e4f96bebe71/speech/0007_35160_36940.wav"
